><w:t>North-West University</w:t></w:r></w:p><w:p w14:paraId="4E7F47FE" w14:textId="63E0FF9F" w:rsidR="003A0ED2" w:rsidRPr="003A0ED2" w:rsidRDefault="003A0ED2" w:rsidP="003A0ED2"><w:pPr><w:jc w:val="center"/><w:rPr><w:i/><w:iCs/><w:sz w:val="20"/><w:szCs w:val="20"/></w:rPr></w:pPr><w:r w:rsidRPr="003A0ED2"><w:rPr><w:i/><w:iCs/><w:sz w:val="20"/><w:szCs w:val="20"/></w:rPr><w:t>South Africa</w:t></w:r></w:p><w:p w14:paraId="101683DF" w14:textId="77777777" w:rsidR="00971C72" w:rsidRDefault="00971C72"/><w:p w14:paraId="3D2EB6BB" w14:textId="13A5FFA9" w:rsidR="00E83D26" w:rsidRDefault="00396009" w:rsidP="007B2090"><w:pPr><w:spacing w:line="360" w:lineRule="auto"/><w:jc w:val="both"/></w:pPr><w:r w:rsidRPr="00396009"><w:t>Today, when I reflect on life and memory before writing, it fe</w:t></w:r><w:r w:rsidR="00612903"><w:t>els</w:t></w:r><w:r w:rsidRPr="00396009"><w:t xml:space="preserve"> directionless. </w:t></w:r><w:r w:rsidR="008A39F6"><w:t>Reflecting</w:t></w:r><w:r w:rsidR="004462BA"><w:t>, I am not entirely sure how I approached critical reflection as part of daily life.</w:t></w:r><w:r w:rsidRPr="00396009"><w:t xml:space="preserve"> </w:t></w:r><w:r w:rsidR="00E45A93"><w:t xml:space="preserve">When accessing these memories, I often wonder how I made decisions, solved, or caused problems or </w:t></w:r><w:r w:rsidR="008A39F6"><w:t>planned</w:t></w:r><w:r w:rsidR="00E45A93"><w:t>.</w:t></w:r><w:r w:rsidRPr="00396009"><w:t xml:space="preserve"> In retrospect, my life before writing lacked coherence. I am uncertain whether this points to a reality grounded in either libertarian or deterministic principles, but writing, for me, offers a sense of clarity and control that was once missing</w:t></w:r><w:r w:rsidR="00A44A4F"><w:t>,</w:t></w:r><w:r w:rsidR="00EF4B50"><w:t xml:space="preserve"> uncovering connections between thoughts and experiences I had not recogni</w:t></w:r><w:r w:rsidR="00FD23C7"><w:t>s</w:t></w:r><w:r w:rsidR="00EF4B50"><w:t>ed before.</w:t></w:r><w:r w:rsidR="0008522D" w:rsidRPr="0008522D"><w:t xml:space="preserve"> </w:t></w:r><w:r w:rsidR="00EF4B50"><w:t xml:space="preserve">Although maturity played a role, I believe writing </w:t></w:r><w:r w:rsidR="008F5681"><w:t>created some sort of structure t</w:t></w:r><w:r w:rsidR="00605599"><w:t>hat enabled</w:t></w:r><w:r w:rsidR="00EF4B50"><w:t xml:space="preserve"> deepened reflecti</w:t></w:r><w:r w:rsidR="00605599"><w:t>on</w:t></w:r><w:r w:rsidR="00EF4B50"><w:t xml:space="preserve"> and critical abilities</w:t></w:r><w:r w:rsidR="00605599"><w:t>.</w:t></w:r><w:r w:rsidR="00CE5926"><w:t xml:space="preserve"> </w:t></w:r><w:r w:rsidR="00E83D26"><w:t>A</w:t></w:r><w:r w:rsidR="00E83D26" w:rsidRPr="00E83D26"><w:t>t times, I wonder how life would have unfolded if I hadn’t discovered the guiding force of writing</w:t></w:r><w:r w:rsidR="00E83D26"><w:t xml:space="preserve">. </w:t></w:r></w:p><w:p w14:paraId="60F76BA2" w14:textId="1200EF73" w:rsidR="00B309FB" w:rsidRDefault="00C505C4" w:rsidP="007B2090"><w:pPr><w:spacing w:line="360" w:lineRule="auto"/><w:jc w:val="both"/></w:pPr><w:r w:rsidRPr="00C505C4"><w:t>The veil of ambiguity started to lift when my writing journey began as a second-year philosophy tutor</w:t></w:r><w:r w:rsidR="006E09D2"><w:t>.</w:t></w:r><w:r w:rsidR="003A0E92"><w:t xml:space="preserve"> </w:t></w:r><w:r w:rsidR="00595D15"><w:t xml:space="preserve">At this stage, reading and writing began to reveal </w:t></w:r><w:r w:rsidR="00590EAF"><w:t>themselves</w:t></w:r><w:r w:rsidR="00595D15"><w:t xml:space="preserve"> not as a task of consuming knowledge for myself but </w:t></w:r><w:r w:rsidR="00590EAF"><w:t xml:space="preserve">as </w:t></w:r><w:r w:rsidR="006844FA"><w:t>a phenomenon that relays information from one to the other – yes, i</w:t></w:r><w:r w:rsidR="00FE1753"><w:t>nterconnectedness.</w:t></w:r><w:r w:rsidR="006E09D2"><w:t xml:space="preserve"> </w:t></w:r><w:r w:rsidR="00910F6B" w:rsidRPr="00910F6B"><w:t>Choosing words is personal, but sharing their value requires selecting them with mutual benefit in mind</w:t></w:r><w:r w:rsidR="00910F6B"><w:t xml:space="preserve">. </w:t></w:r><w:r w:rsidR="00A71B76"><w:t>Thus, I</w:t></w:r><w:r w:rsidR="00EF4B50"><w:t xml:space="preserve"> discovered the profound task of choosing words, as they shaped how students – and myself – received and understood centuries of thought.</w:t></w:r><w:r w:rsidR="006E09D2"><w:t xml:space="preserve"> </w:t></w:r><w:r w:rsidR="003A5CE0"><w:t>However, I continue to discover, recover and uncover the importance of word building (or maybe ‘world</w:t></w:r><w:r w:rsidR="00590EAF"><w:t>-</w:t></w:r><w:r w:rsidR="003A5CE0"><w:t>building’).</w:t></w:r><w:r w:rsidR="009A7381"><w:t xml:space="preserve"> </w:t></w:r></w:p><w:p w14:paraId="49D97951" w14:textId="2C5A1200" w:rsidR="006E7CED" w:rsidRDefault="00E45A93" w:rsidP="007B2090"><w:pPr><w:spacing w:line="360" w:lineRule="auto"/><w:jc w:val="both"/></w:pPr><w:r><w:t xml:space="preserve">Later, I would become a lecturer on </w:t></w:r><w:r w:rsidR="000B103F"><w:t xml:space="preserve">the </w:t></w:r><w:r><w:t>second-year history of philosophy.</w:t></w:r><w:r w:rsidR="00355391"><w:t xml:space="preserve"> Here,</w:t></w:r><w:r w:rsidR="00275A02"><w:t xml:space="preserve"> </w:t></w:r><w:r w:rsidR="00E57F28" w:rsidRPr="00E57F28"><w:t xml:space="preserve">I encountered </w:t></w:r><w:r w:rsidR="00355391"><w:t>another language phenomenon, namely the act of</w:t></w:r><w:r w:rsidR="00E57F28" w:rsidRPr="00E57F28"><w:t xml:space="preserve"> plagiarism. </w:t></w:r><w:r w:rsidR="0057190C"><w:t>Like many others, my initial response was reflexive and focused on addressing the immediate problem.</w:t></w:r><w:r w:rsidR="00E57F28" w:rsidRPr="00E57F28"><w:t xml:space="preserve"> </w:t></w:r><w:r w:rsidR="00331E6E"><w:t>However, this experience marked the beginning of a deeper exploration of the complexities of academic writing as it relates to a 'lack of words.'</w:t></w:r><w:r w:rsidR="00C82233"><w:t xml:space="preserve"> </w:t></w:r><w:r w:rsidR="00331E6E"><w:t>For me, plagiarism, or, more broadly, academic misconduct, was formative in my understanding of how academic language and knowledge are acquired.</w:t></w:r><w:r w:rsidR="002E2ED2"><w:t xml:space="preserve"> </w:t></w:r><w:r w:rsidR="003A5CE0"><w:t xml:space="preserve">I </w:t></w:r><w:r w:rsidR="000B103F"><w:t>realised</w:t></w:r><w:r w:rsidR="003A5CE0"><w:t xml:space="preserve"> that academic misconduct reveals itself as a symptom of an underlying problem that is yet to be disclosed.</w:t></w:r><w:r w:rsidR="005D5BE2"><w:t xml:space="preserve"> </w:t></w:r><w:r w:rsidR="003A5CE0"><w:t>Barriers to learning and producing knowledge are deeply complex and confront individuals with the monumental task of overcoming personal, situational, and even existential challenges.</w:t></w:r><w:r w:rsidR="00910F6B"><w:t xml:space="preserve"> </w:t></w:r></w:p><w:p w14:paraId="50D8AE6D" w14:textId="6F20874D" w:rsidR="00397284" w:rsidRDefault="000B103F" w:rsidP="007B2090"><w:pPr><w:spacing w:line="360" w:lineRule="auto"/><w:jc w:val="both"/></w:pPr><w:r w:rsidRPr="000B103F"><w:lastRenderedPageBreak/><w:t xml:space="preserve">The narrative I propose will trace my journey from a fragmented sense of self to one shaped and refined by writing. It will explore how my early encounters with </w:t></w:r><w:r w:rsidR="008C7B03"><w:t>teaching</w:t></w:r><w:r w:rsidRPr="000B103F"><w:t xml:space="preserve"> prompted a deeper reflection on the complexities of academic writing and its role in learning. Through personal stories, such as guiding students in philosophy and confronting barriers to knowledge, the narrative will weave together moments of disruption and growth. Writing will emerge as the “alchemical process” that transforms confusion into clarity and isolation into interconnectedness.</w:t></w:r><w:r><w:t xml:space="preserve"> </w:t></w:r></w:p><w:p w14:paraId="16974636" w14:textId="77777777" w:rsidR="000B103F" w:rsidRDefault="000B103F" w:rsidP="007B2090"><w:pPr><w:spacing w:line="360" w:lineRule="auto"/><w:jc w:val="both"/></w:pPr></w:p><w:p w14:paraId="528111BD" w14:textId="35491C8A" w:rsidR="007254CC" w:rsidRDefault="00B04744"><w:r><w:t xml:space="preserve"> </w:t></w:r></w:p><w:p w14:paraId="42B33BCB" w14:textId="77777777" w:rsidR="007222D8" w:rsidRDefault="007222D8"/><w:sectPr w:rsidR="007222D8"><w:pgSz w:w="11906" w:h="16838"/><w:pgMar w:top="1440" w:right="1440" w:bottom="1440" w:left="1440" w:header="708" w:footer="708" w:gutter="0"/><w:cols w:space="708"/><w:docGrid w:linePitch="360"/></w:sectPr></w:body></w:document>